reviews_data.review_text: Drinks, service, vibe and music are all perfect. Fav CLT bar/lounge.

I went to Lorem Ipsum a couple of nights ago with two girlfriends and had a great time. I’ll start with the only minor irritation of the evening - we had a reservation for 7, I entered a couple of minutes before seven, waited at the hostess stand, and was never acknowledged. A woman moving around the bar area appeared to make eye contact with me but never said anything. Once my friend entered, we decided to just enter into the bar area and take a table since we hadn’t been acknowledged and that’s when the same woman behind the bar that I’d seen earlier stopped us and asked if we had a res. I didn’t like that. Then she pointed us to a table that had two seats when our res was for three. We asked if we could move a chair over from the next table and she said she would go grab one, but she didn’t grab another chair until after our third friend arrived. She did tell us that she was there alone but honestly that’s not my problem. First impressions are everything and this one turned me off. Thankfully, the rest of the evening was great. Lorem is super vibey and chill. Playlist was love, drinks were tasty, and the atmosphere was quiet enough that we could talk while also vibe to the music. I’d totally come back and hopefully the next time they’re appropriately staffed.

Lorem Ipsum is such a vibe and has a great  selection of cocktails and drinks . From the DJ, Justin, to the servers—Sekani, Nadira, and others—all of them! It is a smaller space, but it’s sufficient for the crowd that come in and out. I hope they expand and can get space for more people to experience the timeless music and vibes. I also spoke to Patrice, who is very pleasant and co-runs the establishment. Truly, it is a hidden gem in CLT. Great drinks, if I forgot to mention! (Florida water and sage burner are my personal favs).

Maybe this will get a response - for my Birthday, I intentionally wanted to support a Black owned business and had heard great things about Lorem Ipsum. I called and left voicemail. I went by there and left my name, #, and the date. I sent email directly to Justin as instructed by the bar tender, and I reached out to one the DJs they use. No response from Justin from any of my attempts. I get being busy but a non responsive business is a bad business plan especially when people are wanting to support. Maybe the goal is to keep Lorem Ipsum a secret 🙊.  If so, message received. Ill be taking my birthday crew to more established venue up the road.
Tasty cocktail and relaxing environment but definitely overpriced

reviews_data.review_text: Justin, his wife, and their team have put together a great bar at Lorem Ipsum. Great cocktails, chill space, and the vibe is great (especially once the DJ turns up later in the evening). Staff is friendly and engaging. Having been a fan of Justin's work at Leah & Louise in the past, great to see this venue carrying on that great mixology. Cocktails are $17 (non-alcs at $11), and they have beer and wine too.

This place is an entire vibe. My friends and I arrived early on a Thursday and we were the only customers. However,  it was still perfect.  The bartender was perfect and thr music was perfect.  I will be back.

Very, very cool spot. Super chill and laid-back. It is close to a Mexican spot and you can bring your food in there and enjoy it with your cocktails. The cocktail menu was amazing. The music was very nice as well. When I was there, there was no Dj, but apparently he was coming later. They had a very good drink. Mix with gin and Mezcal at the time when I went.  I think their menu is rotating for the cocktails. They don’t serve food. Very nice Vibe . Aja was very friendly.
The hype is real - this place has vibes for days. This bar is moody, neo-soul music personified. Attentive staff and an excellent selection of liquors, too.
Best bar in the city.
Very cool place for date and conversation while listening to a variety of nice tunes. Staff is nice and engaging and the atmosphere very nice
Such a cute low key vibe

I went there on a Saturday night. Music was oddly disturbing and loud. I get that it’s a listening bar but a lot of places do a good job on the music. Drinks were fine but service was a little slow given how busy it was. The server partially spilled the drink on me and that did not seem like a great experience.
Felt really rushed and was not comfortable the music was great though.

From the moment I walked in I had a total smile on my face!!!  Lorem Ipsum Listening Bar is an absolute treasure!  I loved the vibe at this bar.  Wonderful atmosphere, chill feeling but upbeat!  Drinks were spot on and service with a personal feel.  We will definately be back!  Loved entirely everything about this place!  It is a hidden gem!
The experience was amazing and the cocktails by Rose were delicious! Thank you for a great evening out on a Sunday!

We popped in for one final drink last night and the vibes were very cool in this little space. All three of us loved our cocktails and service was great. I will have to come back. The “listening bar” area was nicely staged and loved the checks coming out on old vinyl records.
Excellent cocktails, great music, and cozy intimate vibe. 10/10 loved this place, definitely recommend!!
Great drinks.. amazing atmosphere. Energy is right with the music and service this is a hidden gem in charlotte will be regular !

I’m going to sound like a boomer Karen type and I’m not. The service was legitimately just bad.

I walked in, stood at the bar while 3 bartenders stood in a circle talking to each other. One gave me a menu (which I didn’t even ask for or want) and went back to talking. I got one’s attention and ordered a drink with dry vermouth in it, which they said they didn’t have. What kind of cocktail bar can’t make a martini, negroni, or a perfect manhattan? I didn’t want any of their sweet menu items so I ordered a beer. They would not accept cash. Correction — she accepted my $10, at first, while asking “do you need change? < long pause while I stared at her and finally said ‘yes’ > Because we can’t give it.” Then she handed it back to me. It felt like a confrontational way to try to get an undeserved tip. Of course if I would have gotten my very standard cocktail, I would have tipped generously, but I’m not tipping $4 on a $6 can of beer.

Atmosphere was great though! I caught the tail end of a DJ’s set which sounded great, and a guy playing ambient synthesizer music live. I commend the place for a unique concept and great execution on the space. But they desperately need to step up their bar service in an area with so many well-stocked bars within walking distance, and polite and engaging bartenders that accept cash.

10/10 vibes for the people that want to be out but not overwhelmed. Great music, great drinks, great service, great atmosphere!
We will for sure be back!

Lorem Ipsum has quickly become my go-to bar, and it’s easy to see why. The staff here are warm and welcoming, and they go out of their way to check in with you when they recognize you—a personal touch that makes you feel right at home.

This place attracts a certain kind of person, and I’ve had some of the most interesting conversations with people from all walks of life. It’s a spot where you can swap stories and create memories, all while enjoying a beautifully crafted drink.

Lorem Ipsum isn’t a place to turn up; it’s where you go to relax, unwind, and engage in thoughtful conversation. There aren’t many spots in Charlotte that offer the unique energy that Lorem Ipsum brings to the table. Whether you’re with a group or just looking for a solo drink, this bar is a perfect choice.

Small and quaint. Positive vibes, easy listening music provided by a DJ., Staff pleasant and accommodating.

Great vibe and drinks, very intimate. The service was a 10
Nothing but love for this establishment! Even though no food is offered, you can BYOF or Door Dash. Ambiance, drinks are 10/10. A true listening experience… you must visit while you’re in the area.
Dope spot for drinks and great music. Staff is great!!

I ended up at Lorem Ipsum tonight, visiting for the first time. It's a great place to have drinks and listen to some fantastic music. The DJ is amazing, playing a mix of both old-school and new-school hits. The crowd is very diverse--young, old, white, black--everyone's there for the same great vibe. Just to prepare, parking is somewhat limited.

Lorem Ipsum Listening Bar is an absolute treasure! From the moment you step in, you can feel the love and attention to detail the founders have poured into this place. The atmosphere is incredible, with a perfect blend of cozy and chic. They even deliver your check in a CD case, a fun and unique touch.

The drinks are flavorful and expertly crafted, adding to the overall experience. The music selection is always on point, and the seamless transitions between tracks keep the vibe just right. A great movie usually plays on the projector, adding an extra layer of ambiance.

It's the perfect spot to relax and unwind without any fuss. Whether you're there to catch up with friends or enjoy solo time, Lorem Ipsum Listening Bar never disappoints. Highly recommend!
Very chill lounge.  Awesome cocktails. Rose, Justin and Jefferson will take care of you.
Nadira rocks!  Awesome cocktails and great vibe!

I attended Lorem Ipsum on my birthday and then again tonight! The service is always amazing, the music is always a vibe and it was great that our bartenders remembered us. I love that it is intimate and can carry on with meaningful conversation while you are there. The drinks are amazing and strong, ans the atmosphere is always warm and welcoming. My husband and I have made this place our weekly date night spot. If you are thinking about going… do it you won’t regret it❤️

How dope is this spot? It's quaint and cute. The vibe is intimate, and the drinks are skrong. I had the Robinson augmented to be a bit sweeter, and it was delicious. It gave me a strong calm.

The ambiance was dope. It's intimate and chic. You can have titillating convo and a great cocktail.
Such an amazing experience and amazing drinks!
Laidback unpretentious vibe.

Went here with two friends for the first time the first Friday of January 2024. Amazing spot for people who want to be classy and grown. Loved meeting people who were visiting Charlotte from other states. Everyone was so chill and relaxed. Low-key, no drama, beautiful atmosphere. Drinks were well crafted. I have not had an experience like this in a very long time. I plan on bringing an out-of-town guest here next week.

OMG! When I tell you Lorem Ipsum is what Charlotte needed all along. I wouldn't be lying to you. I am highly impressed with this black owned listening bar; from the alternative R&B, neo soul and etc, playing in the background if the owner isn't DJing, to the service of the staff, to the cocktails being crafted,  the cozy seating/environment and the projector playing black classics or something random. I am speechless. I have recommended this place to at least 5 people with similar taste in music. I've been several times and plan to continue to unwind, enjoy some good music, and have a glass of wine. This is a very small establishment so much like the other reviews if you're coming on a weekend; you're bound to wait. However, there is a restaurant down the hall. Join the wait list and grab a bite. They do not serve food at all. The drinks can be a bit costly but much like every other place within the area. They are inside of the Hotel Refuge, so do not be alarmed. All in all, support this black business! Even if it wasn't black, support them anyway because this was by far a dope and unique concept Charlotte has needed for a long time.
Great experience! The drinks were amazing.

We had the best experience at Lorem Ipsum! There was an issue with their waitlist, so we never got the text that a table was ready. The staff was so nice about it, they gave us our first round free. The drinks, atmosphere, and music were all incredible. Definitely worth the visit!
Cute spot, with a chill vibe and pretty good drinks.
Grown and sexy meets vibe worthy cocktails and groovy bass heavy jamz

Lorem Ipsum is nice place for a date or  night out with a couple of friends wanting to catch up.
Small intimate space with great cocktails and chill music playing in the background. You can listen to the music and each other.

I enjoyed my visit to Lorem Ipsum. Great vibes,  drinks, and service.  Great spot for after dinner drinks, catching up with friends, or solo.  They dont serve food so I couldn't rate that. The music was nice but wasn't blaring so you are able to have conversation without yelling.  Due to size and seating, I would not recommend for large groups. 4 or less would be ok.

Talk about a vibe inside ! This is such a cool spot ! Definetly somewhere you would want to take a first date ! I love the concept of it being a listening bar & you can even bring your own vinyl . Lorem Ipsum is located inside of a hotel in the plaza Midwood area called Refugee .

Inside is a very dim setting with relaxing music from Lo fi to Luther Vandross & all the great’s. Theirs also an outside patio area . One thing I thought was very cool is the server brings your check in a cd case.

I recommend anyone looking for grown laid back dates vibes this is the place to be.
Small intimate setting with cozy music. Great for date night without the crowd. Drinks were very amazing!!! "Now, let's keep this a secret between us... Ok!" Lol

This was a true definition of a vibe. Great way to start or end your night. We chose to start our night and it was definitely worth it. It was our first time I will say I loved the spirit less options. These are great craft cocktails! Will be back for a date night.
Easily the coolest new concept in Charlotte. Great music, incredible drinks, top notch atmosphere. 100% must check out.
Great, relaxing vibe. Very cozy

Overall good spot

Recommend 🫡🫡

Definitely a spot you should go to. Drinks , atmosphere, music was everything. A cool chill spot to socialize. I’ll absolutely be going again.

I am highly impressed with this black owned listening bar; from the alternative R&B, neo soul and etc, playing in the background if the owner isn't DJing, to the service of the staff, to the cocktails being crafted,  the cozy seating/environment and the projector playing black classics or something random. I am speechless. I have recommended this place to at least 5 people with similar taste in music. I've been several times and plan to continue to unwind, enjoy some good music, and have a glass of wine. This is a very small establishment so much like the other reviews if you're coming on a weekend; you're bound to wait. However, there is a restaurant down the hall. Join the wait list and grab a bite. They do not serve food at all. The drinks can be a bit costly but much like every other place within the area. They are inside of the Hotel Refuge, so do not be alarmed. All in all, support this black business! Even if it wasn't black, support them anyway because this was by far a dope and unique concept Charlotte has needed for a long time.
